{"tid":992733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7歲男罕見骨肉瘤惡化 赴美求醫眾籌400萬元","createTime":"2019-01-23T11:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T05:31:52.000Z","uid":65024,"like":5,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"67b934ed03fcb574e77ca7a839290fb328368c4b","tid":992733,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190123/large/1548223047_3ad6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190123%2Flarge%2F1548223047_3ad6.png&h=68cfcf3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190123/small/1548223616_d2fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190123%2Fsmall%2F1548223616_d2fc.jpg&h=fdfa39ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190123/small/1548223616_6a8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190123%2Fsmall%2F1548223616_6a8f.jpg&h=7d7bf485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7歲男童患罕見骨肉瘤，急需籌400萬元治療。男童李羿廷（Aidan）去年8月，因左膝關節疼痛，父母帶他到醫院求醫，確診十分罕見的擴散性骨肉瘤，接受化療後，病情仍惡化，癌細胞擴散，已不能動手術切除。Aidan的父母不願放棄，決定帶他赴美求醫，然而治療費用遠超預算，他們盡耗積蓄及親友支持所得的100萬元，僅夠首3個月的化療，餘下9個月另需300至400萬港元。Aidan的母親Peggie在facebook發文眾籌，盼有心人幫助兒子度過難關。<br />\n<br />\nPeggie形容Aidan在患病前，品學兼優，乖巧獨立，性格樂天，在老師眼裏也是好學生、好榜樣。她說作為母親，有難以言傳的壓力，這筆醫療費用對一般家庭而言，亦是天文數字，「但我們仍然相信，希望在人間」，即使只得一絲希望，亦會堅持到底。<br />\n<br />\n她稱，Aidan最初在香港治療，惟醫生告知，本港僅有4款治療骨肉瘤的化療藥物，當時已用其中3款，若效果不佳，已無藥可治，會改為紓緩治療。夫婦倆輾轉得知，友人兒子患另一種罕見癌症，赴美求醫後康復，重燃一家人的希望。她去年底帶同Aidan，到美國專治癌症的MD Anderson Cancer Center求醫，任職消防員的丈夫，則留港照顧10歲女兒。因Aidan的病情日趨嚴重，醫生認為應立即做化療，必要時再做放射治療，預計為期1年，其間另會考慮為他做免疫治療，或為新藥做臨床實驗。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ngaiting.li.3/posts/117625342630166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fngaiting.li.3%2Fposts%2F117625342630166&d=aJoDg7%2FdIljMrna1Ylq5yAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=907aaea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ngaiting.li.3/posts/117625342630166</a>"},{"pid":"b8cbb5a9c2f7468c3ef28abbfab8ee3956ab4c34","tid":992733,"uid":1255,"like":40,"dislike":6,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"借錢囉 使乜籌"},{"pid":"79927999982063c2cf9d419acf96b22f9e06394d","tid":992733,"uid":76776,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"170ea1aafce5ff40846753b4bdba23c327e729bd","tid":992733,"uid":159876,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:34:44.000Z","msg":"阿豬阿狗都籌錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7896573382ab15af9d9f650fac4748c81bf99e73","tid":992733,"uid":37661,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"品學兼優真係個個都係架喎。"},{"pid":"0070c980b02bf13cbee08e96ec33b58581d26526","tid":992733,"uid":182499,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:36:08.000Z","msg":"香港冇咁多大愛撚 籌400百萬有啲難度 試下問李生可能有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b974fcf201157d4b54dec66156e6edbe229c93ed","tid":992733,"uid":192190,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"點解個個病童都係品學兼優，乖巧獨立，性格樂天，在老師眼裏也是好學生、好榜樣?<br />\n係咪唔叻唔乖唔聽話就唔值得救?"},{"pid":"cce3874a5bda4a15a7eb1442d89045a1bbd917db","tid":992733,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1965938556ac7c84a9ef2fbf9107b08738f9287","tid":992733,"uid":65024,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"見facebook留言好撚多人捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106d316e7aa9ce19ac955857c3f15c07be9d7570","tid":992733,"uid":37661,"like":22,"dislike"